scenes.description: Hololive talents performing 'Our Bright Parade' on stage.
Credits roll showing the cast and setlist.

subtitles.original: Parade, Parade, Parade！
subtitles.english: Parade, Parade, Parade!

subtitles.original: 探しにゆく スタートは何度だって
subtitles.english: We go searching, we can start over any number of times.

subtitles.original: ただ 独り言続いた
subtitles.english: I just kept talking to myself.

subtitles.original: ただ 始まりたくて走った
subtitles.english: I just ran because I wanted to begin.

subtitles.original: 遠く 暗がりに灯った
subtitles.english: A light lit up in the distant darkness.

subtitles.original: それは 眩しすぎた名前
subtitles.english: That name was too dazzling.

subtitles.original: それは 優しすぎる思い出
subtitles.english: Those memories were too gentle.

subtitles.original: もっと 近づけと手を伸ばした
subtitles.english: I wanted to get closer, so I reached out my hand.

subtitles.original: 思いがけず結び合った
subtitles.english: Unexpectedly, we connected.

subtitles.original: ほら 今 迷子は僕らになった
subtitles.english: Look, now the lost children have become "us".

subtitles.original: Parade, Parade, Parade！
subtitles.english: Parade, Parade, Parade!

subtitles.original: 輝くんだよ
subtitles.english: It shines!

subtitles.original: 悔しさも愛しさも連れておいで
subtitles.english: Bring along your frustrations and your beloved feelings.

subtitles.original: 風 夢 羽 飛び立てるさ
subtitles.english: Wind, dreams, wings, we can take flight.

subtitles.original: ささやかな祈りは光 終わりなき日差し
subtitles.english: A humble prayer is light, an endless sunshine.

subtitles.original: 君も見つけたこと 胸を張れるよ
subtitles.english: You can be proud of what you found too.

subtitles.original: ここから これから Our Bright Parade, Parade！
subtitles.english: From here, from now on, Our Bright Parade, Parade!

subtitles.original: まだ頼りない横顔 歌おう
subtitles.english: Let's sing with our still unreliable profiles.

subtitles.original: 恥ずかしくなんてないよ
subtitles.english: There's nothing to be ashamed of.

subtitles.original: 誰も解けないイマジナリー
subtitles.english: An imaginary that no one can solve.

subtitles.original: いつかまた会えるおまじない
subtitles.english: A magic spell to meet again someday.

subtitles.original: あの日ゼロに始まったストーリー
subtitles.english: The story that began from zero that day.

subtitles.original: 数えきれない言の葉
subtitles.english: Countless words.

subtitles.original: 数えるような想いじゃないさ
subtitles.english: It's not a feeling that can be counted.

subtitles.original: ほら 今 僕らをひとつと呼ぼう
subtitles.english: Look, let's call "us" one now.

subtitles.original: Parade, Parade, Parade！
subtitles.english: Parade, Parade, Parade!

subtitles.original: 美しいんだよ
subtitles.english: It's beautiful!

subtitles.original: 許し合える刹那 夜はきらめく
subtitles.english: In the fleeting moment we forgive each other, the night sparkles.

subtitles.original: 雨 晴れ カレイド またとない空
subtitles.english: Rain, sun, kaleidoscope, a sky like no other.

subtitles.original: 相応しい旅路とは
subtitles.english: A fitting journey is...

subtitles.original: 君とあることさ
subtitles.english: being with you.

subtitles.original: 君とあることなんだ
subtitles.english: It truly is being with you.

subtitles.original: ただいまを聞けば おかえりって叫ぶよ
subtitles.english: If I hear "I'm home", I'll shout "Welcome back!"

subtitles.original: 当たり前じゃないか
subtitles.english: Isn't that obvious?

subtitles.original: Parade, Parade, Parade！
subtitles.english: Parade, Parade, Parade!

subtitles.original: 輝くんだよ
subtitles.english: It shines!

subtitles.original: 暗がりを満たすのは君だ 僕だ
subtitles.english: The one filling the darkness is you, it's me!

subtitles.original: Parade, Parade, Parade！
subtitles.english: Parade, Parade, Parade!

subtitles.original: 輝くんだよ
subtitles.english: It shines!

subtitles.original: 悔しさも愛しさも連れておいで
subtitles.english: Bring along your frustrations and your beloved feelings.

subtitles.original: 風 夢 羽 飛び立てるさ
subtitles.english: Wind, dreams, wings, we can take flight.

subtitles.original: ささやかな祈りは光 終わりなき日差し
subtitles.english: A humble prayer is light, an endless sunshine.

subtitles.original: 君と飛び込んでゆく 素敵なスタートさ
subtitles.english: Diving in with you, it's a wonderful start.

subtitles.original: ここから これから Our Bright Parade, Parade！
subtitles.english: From here, from now on, Our Bright Parade, Parade!

subtitles.english: Our Bright Parade, Parade!
